title: Ebro In The Morning - Omarion Verzuz Mario + Rosenberg & Lupe Fiasco's Vague Beef

Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 6/24/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing the Lupe's alleged beef with Rosenberg, last night's Omarion VERZUZ Mario, and NBA Draft Fashion. 

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
